</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_397" id="198r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_397_r1l1">Johanſen <expan>Lantgraf<ex>en</ex></expan> cʒum <expan>Lewchtemb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_397_r1l2">Grafen cʒü Halls </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_397_r1l3"><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> / Als Jr vns <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt vnd begert daʒ vvir </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_397_r1l4">ew <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchreıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>ſolt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / von vvandel <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> bey vns etc . laſſen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_397_r1l5">wir ewr gnad wıſſen / daʒ vnſer gewonheit nicht ıſt / daʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_397_r1l6">vvir ſöliche v̈ber land <expan>ſchreıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / . Dann wo es an vns braht </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_397_r1l7">wirdt / So ercʒelen wir das müntlıchen den die man <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_397_r1l8">darvmb cʒü vns ſchıckt / vnd alſo <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vvir / das dem <expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_397_r1l9"><expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> vns <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> brief braht hat <expan>müntlıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vvol ercʒelt vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_397_r1l10">geſagt / . Ob <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> ewr gnade an Jm nicht ein genüg <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_397_r1l11">wolt / . wen Jr <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> cʒu vns ſchıckt der des <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_397_r1l12"><expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> vns begert / . Dem wöllen vvir das aber <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> müntlıch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_397_r1l13">ercʒelen vnd <expan>vnt<ex>er</ex>richten</expan> / . vnd vvo wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_397_r1l14"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> ıj̃ . <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> <expan>Epıph<ex>anie</ex></expan> . </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_397" id="198r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Johansen, <expan>lantgraf<ex>en</ex></expan> czum
                                <expan>Lewchtemb<ex>er</ex>g</expan>, grafen czü Halls</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan>, als ir uns
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt und begert, daz wir ew
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schreib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>solt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von wandel <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> bey
                        uns etc., lassen wir ewr gnad wissen, daz unser gewonheit nicht ist, daz wir
                        söliche über land <expan>schreib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. Dann wo es an uns braht
                        wirdt, so erczelen wir das müntlichen den, die man
                            <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> darumb czü uns schickt, und also
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir das dem
                            <expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> uns
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> brief braht hat,
                                <expan>müntlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wol erczelt und gesagt. Ob
                                <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> ewr gnade an im nicht ein genüg
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wolt, wen ir
                            <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> czu uns schickt, der des
                                <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> uns begert, dem wöllen wir das aber
                                <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> müntlich erczelen und
                                <expan>unt<ex>er</ex>richten</expan>. Und wo wir
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> ii <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>epiph<ex>anie</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
